 use of Federal-aid highways, a State\n\t\t\t or local law enforcement officer from using the race or ethnicity of the driver\n\t\t\t or passengers to any degree in making routine or spontaneous law enforcement\n\t\t\t decisions, such as ordinary traffic stops on Federal-aid highways.", "@entity-type": "act", "#text": "subsection (a)(1)", "@value": "Racial Profiling Prevention Act/s:2/ss:a/p:1", "@proposed": "true"}, "#text": "To meet the\n\t\t\t requirement of ", "@display-inline": "yes-display-inline"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n          ", "#text": "(1)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n          ", "#text": "In\n\t\t\t general"}, "#text": "\n          ", "@id": "H155F0EBAFBD1467B8D57E88115FADF54"}, {"#tail": "\n      ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t", "#text": "Nothing in this subsection shall alter the\n\t\t\t manner in which a State or local law enforcement officer considers race or\n\t\t\t ethnicity whenever there is trustworthy information, relevant to the locality\n\t\t\t or time frame, that links persons of a particular race or ethnicity to an\n\t\t\t identified criminal incident, scheme, or organization.", "@display-inline": "yes-display-inline"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n          ", "#text": "(2)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n          ", "#text": "Limitation"}, "#text": "\n          ", "@id": "H35855F7165E8412A898DC076B7095C45"}], "#text": "\n        ", "@id": "HF4EFDB01EF06494DB46A613D014B8C30"}, {"#tail": "\n      ", "enum": {"#tail": "\n        ", "#text": "(d)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t", "#text": "Limitations"}, "paragraph": [{"#tail": "\n        ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t", "#text": "The total amount of\n\t\t\t grants made to a State under this section in a fiscal year may not exceed 5\n\t\t\t percent of the amount made available to carry out this section in the fiscal\n\t\t\t year.", "@display-inline": "yes-display-inline"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n          ", "#text": "(1)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n          ", "#text": "Maximum amount\n\t\t\t of grants"}, "#text": "\n          ", "@id": "HC41870FA802E4730ADA962C7F2022938"}, {"#tail": "\n      ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t", "{http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml}entity-ref": {"#tail": " in more than 2 fiscal years.", "@entity-type": "act", "#text": "subsection (a)(2)", "@value": "Racial Profiling Prevention Act/s:2/ss:a/p:2", "@proposed": "true"}, "#text": "A State may not receive a grant under\n\t\t\t ", "@display-inline": "yes-display-inline"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n          ", "#text": "(2)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n          ", "#text": "Eligibility"}, "#text": "\n          ", "@id": "H820E8BAFF7CC4A76B9428A5934901BAA"}], "#text": "\n        ", "@id": "HC177E6150EAD4E5F905D7EC5072D9127"}, {"#tail": "\n    ", "enum": {"#tail": "\n        ", "#text": "(e)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t", "#text": "Authorization of\n\t\t\t appropriations"}, "paragraph": [{"#tail": "\n        ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t", "#text": "\n            ", "{http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml}entity": {"#tail": "\n          ", "{http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml}funds-and-year": {"#tail": ".", "#text": "$7,500,000 for each of fiscal years 2013\n\t\t\t through 2017", "@amount": "7500000", "@year": "2013, 2014, 2015, 2016, 2017"}, "@entity-type": "auth-auth-approp", "#text": "There is authorized\n\t\t\t to be appropriated from the ", "{http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml}property": [{"#tail": " (other than the Mass Transit\n\t\t\t Account) ", "#text": "Highway Trust Fund", "@name": "funds-source"}, {"#tail": " ", "{http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml}entity-ref": {"#tail": "\n              ", "@entity-type": "act", "#text": "this section", "@value": "Racial Profiling Prevention Act/s:2", "@proposed": "true"}, "#text": "to carry out ", "@name": "purpose"}]}, "@display-inline": "yes-display-inline"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n          ", "#text": "(1)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n          ", "#text": "In\n\t\t\t general"}, "#text": "\n          ", "@id": "H7DAD30627FB1456194D7596D5FE7B74